  "title": "Barista / Customer Experience",
  "description": "<p><em>We are a collective of F&B professionals, innately hospitable and guided by an unwavering sense of care and devotion—to our craft, our guests, and one another. With passionate expertise, we elevate every guest experience, enveloping our guests in our art of Memorable Hospitality. Our leaders lead with respect and empower with thoughtful intention, cultivating a culture where the expertise of each team member is celebrated. In doing so, we inspire our teams to extend that same depth of valued recognition and grace to every guest we serve.</em></p><p><br /></p><p>If you're a empathetic individual who is excited to work with like-minded people and to punch above your weight towards a more successful F&B group career, we would be happy to meet up with you.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Why you will love working with us:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience learning & crafting matcha beverages.</li><li>Love delighting our customers, learning professional barista & parfait skills.</li><li>Enjoy people interactions and spreading joy.</li><li>Fast & Fun — Thrive in a dynamic, team-oriented environment.</li><li>Learn & be mentored — By proven industry leaders who lead by empathy and example.</li><li>Easy to commute — We are just a few steps from Promenade MRT station.</li><li>No experience? No problem! We train passionate enthusiasts.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess the skills of a qualified barista.</li><li>A positive and empathetic attitude towards work.</li><li>Objective-based communication and working style.</li><li>Fluent in English, excels in communication.</li></ul>",
