    "description": "<p>In the cafe where yasuragi is kept,<br>\nWe wander into moments of gentle, timeless grace—<br>\nOur hurried steps surrender to a soft, unhurried cadence,<br>\nAnd hearts find solace in a lull of inner peace.<br>\n<br>\nHere, every taste and touch is a tribute to wellbeing,<br>\nA celebration of nourishment both for the body and soul.<br>\nAmid the whispers of friends and quiet smiles,<br>\nThe clamour of the world fades into a serene refrain,<br>\nInviting us to savour the poetry of calm and harmony.<br>\n<br>\nA sanctuary born from the art of mindful hospitality,<br>\nWhere every guest is cradled in the warm embrace<br>\nOf pleasing cuisine and memories that linger like a cherished melody.</p>",
